description:
Andy Garner, IAEA Seibersdorf Laboratory Coordinator, contributed a Norway Maple tree (acer platanoides) as he led the ReNuAL laboratories modernization from 2013 to 2023. 

Rafael Mariano Grossi, IAEA Director-General, together with Najat Mokhtar, IAEA Deputy Director-General and Head of the Department of Nuclear Sciences and Applications, and other IAEA Senior Officials pose for photos with Andy Garner who will be retiring at the end of the week. IAEA Seibersdorf, Austria. 3 October 2023

Photo Credit: Dean Calma / IAEA
